{"tid":1436473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(分化警報) 千萬不要阻止「機場」示威者唱歌","createTime":"2019-08-09T09:54:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T12:52:21.000Z","uid":134071,"like":43,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b58b47a92faff7822f59b38d4caa2fcf35c489f7","tid":1436473,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:54:39.000Z","msg":"機場有位中佬彈&quot;海闊天空&quot;， 好多人好不安，有部分人仲話要阻人唱歌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1436304/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1436304/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n明白大家感受，但千萬不要阻止「機場」示威者唱歌<br />\n<br />\n1）如果佢無阻其他人， 就唔駛阻止佢唱歌。要尊重手足既自由。<br />\n2）貿貿然阻佢唱歌，係「大台」行為，會俾港共跟cctvb一個難得機會去抹黑示威者。<br />\n3）兄弟爬山，各自努力。人地無干預你， 你都無謂干預人地。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/wby97NC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwby97NC.png&h=96bfb475&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f768db32a02f6a78d4302c26c480b8aa947be2e9","tid":1436473,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:55:07.000Z","msg":"小心分化手段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d811f59327a8f3275c9419e11f94524de64343ad","tid":1436473,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:55:28.000Z","msg":"大家加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03f624749a0c54cf8447bd497230f2834b15a0d5","tid":1436473,"uid":263161,"like":10,"dislike":10,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:55:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e21161a7d1dfa04bff895d95a04381b6f7d6c60","tid":1436473,"uid":134071,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"03f624749a0c54cf8447bd497230f2834b15a0d5","tid":1436473,"uid":263161,"like":10,"dislike":10,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:55:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0